# Ex 8 - temperatura sem campo value

### adicionar stub
POST http://localhost:2525/imposters/3000/stubs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stub": {
    "predicates": [
      {"equals": {"method": "POST", "path": "/api/temperature", "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}}},
      {"not": {"contains": {"body": "value"}}}
    ],
    "responses": [
      {"is": {"statusCode": 400, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"error": "missing_field", "message": "o campo value é obrigatório"}}}
    ]
  }
}

### testar sem value
POST http://localhost:3000/api/temperature
Content-Type: application/json

{"sensor_id": 1}

#-----------------------------------------------------

# Ex 9 - temperatura com campo value

### adicionar stub
POST http://localhost:2525/imposters/3000/stubs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stub": {
    "predicates": [
      {"equals": {"method": "POST", "path": "/api/temperature", "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}}},
      {"contains": {"body": "value"}}
    ],
    "responses": [
      {"is": {"statusCode": 201, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"status": "created", "message": "medição registada com sucesso"}}}
    ]
  }
}

### testar com value
POST http://localhost:3000/api/temperature
Content-Type: application/json

{"sensor_id":1,"value":23.5}

