# Ex 12 - autenticação com token

### adicionar stub sucesso
POST http://localhost:2525/imposters/3000/stubs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stub": {
    "predicates": [
      {"equals": {"method": "POST", "path": "/api/auth", "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}}},
      {"deepEquals": {"body": {"username": "user1", "password": "pass1"}}}
    ],
    "responses": [
      {"is": {"statusCode": 200, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"token": "validtoken", "expires_in": 3600}}}
    ]
  }
}

### adicionar stub falha
POST http://localhost:2525/imposters/3000/stubs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stub": {
    "predicates": [
      {"equals": {"method": "POST", "path": "/api/auth"}}
    ],
    "responses": [
      {"is": {"statusCode": 401, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"error": "invalid_credentials"}}}
    ]
  }
}

### testar credenciais certas
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth
Content-Type: application/json

{"username":"user1","password":"pass1"}

### testar credenciais erradas
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth
Content-Type: application/json

{"username":"hacker","password":"1234"}

