# Ex 13 - perfil protegido com token

### adicionar stub com token válido
POST http://localhost:2525/imposters/3000/stubs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stub": {
    "predicates": [
      {"equals": {"method": "GET", "path": "/api/profile", "headers": {"Authorization": "Bearer validtoken"}}}
    ],
    "responses": [
      {"is": {"statusCode": 200, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"username": "user1", "email": "user1@exemplo.com"}}}
    ]
  }
}

### adicionar stub sem token ou token inválido
POST http://localhost:2525/imposters/3000/stubs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stub": {
    "predicates": [
      {"equals": {"method": "GET", "path": "/api/profile"}}
    ],
    "responses": [
      {"is": {"statusCode": 403, "headers": {"Content-Type": "application/json"}, "body": {"error": "forbidden"}}}
    ]
  }
}

### testar com token válido
GET http://localhost:3000/api/profile
Authorization: Bearer validtoken

### testar sem token
GET http://localhost:3000/api/profile

